           SPELL=iceme
         VERSION=1.0.0
          SOURCE=$SPELL-$VERSION.tar.gz
SOURCE_DIRECTORY=$BUILD_DIRECTORY/$SPELL-$VERSION
   SOURCE_URL[0]=http://download.sourceforge.net/$SPELL/$SOURCE
        WEB_SITE=http://iceme.sourceforge.net
         ENTERED=20020330
         UPDATED=20020330
           SHORT="iceme is a menu editor for the icewm window manager."
cat << EOF
A graphical menu editor for IceWM written in Python and GTK.

Features

    * Tree editing with Drag'n'Drop and Cut'n'Paste
    * Shortcut editor
    * Icon selection dialog
    * Tries to mimic IceWM's idea of getting icon resources as closely as possible
    * Edit the "menu", "programs", "toolbar" and "keys" files
    * You can either edit the local menu in your home or the global menu
    * GPL
EOF
